-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--- Copy a table, including sub-tables.
-- Make a new table, copying key->value from source table.
-- @param table
-- @return new table
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
function CrLua.Table.copy(table)
    assert(type(table) == 'table')

